4df2fbee0803137544127cefbef4c0edbcd0772de604bcdfbb9f13a802ab36106276842cdbb3f2df4677a87080274dad3380143f7c3a0da9d10eb7ea3a4014a6  0001-fix-cmake-dir.patch
"
